dcterms:description: A dataset constructed using real-world data from an international airport, consisting of nine groups of observation data collected at nine closely distributed stations and one group of NWP data for the airfield. The data are hourly time series of weather variables collected from 02:00:00, Mar. 2018 to 23:00:00, Sep. 2019 with a total of 13,176 time points.
dcterms:title: Real-world dataset from an international airport
